title: 593. Gregory Rousseau on His Decision to Opt Out & the Art of Pass Rushing
itunes:title: 593. Gregory Rousseau on His Decision to Opt Out & the Art of Pass Rushing
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys discuss North Dakota State QB Trey Lance's one-game showcase this weekend against Central Arkansas and also the college games they're looking forward to watching this week (1:02). After that, University of Miami defensive end Gregory Rousseau joins, as he talks about his decision to opt out from the college season, what he looks for when he's studying an opponent, his recruiting process, who inspires him and more (6:05).
